metadata.name: Thicc Frens #1
metadata.description: 5,555 sassy Thicc dogs will help you get thicc through daily staking rewards, true companions for your metaverse journey. These cheeky NFTs come in 30 different breeds, all of which have well endowed Thicc butts. There are over 300 unique attributes including tiny frens, hats, hair, accessories, mouths, eyes and backgrounds. Each dog has a rarity value that determines how much $THICC token it'll earn per day when staked (Common, Uncommon and Rare). Adopt a thicc dog and start earning $THICC today!
